Question: Which top 20 driver created the shortest lap time ever record in a Formula_1 race? Please give them full names.

Prediction_0.1: SELECT CONCAT(d.forename, ' ', d.surname) AS full_name, MIN(l.time) AS shortest_lap_time FROM drivers d JOIN lapTimes l ON d.driverId = l.driverId GROUP BY d.driverId, d.forename, d.surname ORDER BY shortest_lap_time ASC LIMIT 20
